<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Services - Tambola Game Provider</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/common.css">
    <style>
        /* Services Section Styling */
        .services {
            background: var(--background-gradient);
            padding: 5rem 0;
        }

        .services h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        }

        .services p {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: white;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .services .container {
            max-width: 960px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Pricing Section */
        .pricing {
            background: #121212;
            padding: 4rem 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .pricing h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .pricing p {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            color: white;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .pricing .btn-contact {
            background: var(--primary-color);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .pricing .btn-contact:hover {
            background: var(--secondary-color);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background: var(--footer-gradient);
            color: var(--primary-color);
            padding: 2rem 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <%- include('partials/_nav') %>

        <!-- Services Section -->
        <section class="services">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="mb-5">
                    <h2>Our Services</h2>
                    <p>We provide comprehensive and customizable tambola game solutions, catering to both individual
                        players
                        and large event organizers. Here are some of the key services we offer:</p>
                </div>
                <!-- Service Cards -->
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="card bg-success bg-gradient" style="background: var(--card-gradient);">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title text-bg-light">Game Hosting</h5>
                                <p class="card-text" style="color: white;">Host virtual tambola games with ease. Our
                                    platform provides everything you need to run a smooth and fun-filled session.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="card bg-info bg-gradient">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title text-bg-light">Custom Themes</h5>
                                <p class="card-text" style="color: white;">Make your game stand out with
                                    personalized
                                    themes. Tailor the look and feel of your game to match your event or occasion.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="card bg-warning bg-gradient">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title text-bg-light">Real-Time Analytics</h5>
                                <p class="card-text" style="color: white;">Get real-time analytics of the game, track
                                    the progress, and instantly notify winners. All in one place!</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Pricing Section -->
        <section class="card-gradient p-5 mb-5">
            <div class="container text-center">
                <h2>Custom Pricing</h2>
                <p>We understand that every event is unique, which is why we offer customizable pricing based on your
                    requirements. Whether you’re hosting a small private game or organizing a large-scale event, we’re
                    here to provide the best experience at a price that fits your budget.</p>
                <p>Contact us today to discuss your specific needs and receive a personalized quote.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-info">Get in Touch</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <%- include('partials/_footer') %>

            <!-- Bootstrap JS and dependencies -->
            <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>